The initial population is a set of potential solutions which obeys the restricted conditions described in Equation 25. The size of population is denoted as L and then the initial population E0 is represented as E0={S1,S2,⋯,SL}. Sℓ=Aℓ,pan,Eℓ,Bmax\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
